(2017-02-01 07:56:33) Angel: MGB is a tri-city model program (Dubai- Sydney- Singapore). The candidate with 0 to 3 years of full time work experience can apply for the MGB program. It is 16 months program (12 Academics +4 Internship)We have 3 intakes every year Jan, May and Sept. Eligibility - GMAT 650+ or CAT 80%ile+ or SPJAT 80%ile+. (2017-02-13 07:45:02) Angel: MGB is a tri-city model program (Dubai- Sydney- Singapore). The candidate with 0 to 3 years of full time work experience can apply for the MGB program. It is 16 months program (12 Academics +4 Internship)We have 3 intakes every year Jan, May and Sept. Eligibility - GMAT 650+ or CAT 80%ile+ or SPJAT 80%ile+. You will be called for evaluation round if you have any one of these scores.
(2017-02-13 07:45:10) Angel: http://www.spjain.org/programs/postgraduate/mgb
